    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "counselors just tell you to cut back on stuff i already cut everything. there's nothing left to cut. it's just like a weight that gets heavier every single day. i'm just so tired of fighting a battle that's already lost. when you look at it from the outside, it just seems like there's no point in dragging this out when the outcome is already decided. it wouldn't even be a tragedy, just... an end to the noise.",
